    "body": "It seems that the engine API does not expose enough information to make `--exitwhensynced` work in all cases. In scenarios where the CL itself is also syncing, we will not trigger an internal 'sync' event, and thus the 'sync' will never be considered finished.\r\n\r\nHowever, the flag will work in other cases. So at the moment, it can be seen as a best-effort kind of feature. After some internal discussion, we are unsure if it can be improved at all.",
